               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480131-name-1076" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18480131-name-1076" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480131-name-1076" type="surname" value="SPINK"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480131-name-1076" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN SPINK</persName>
                  </hi>. I am plumber, at Nine Elms. The prisoner was in my ser<lb></lb>vice—Spice came to me, and I missed some lead from my shop—it had been put away in a basket—it has been found, and matched by the man who laid it—it is mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18480131-name-1077" type="witnessName">
