                        <interp inst="t18480131-name-1077" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES MULLINGER</persName>
                  </hi>. I was employed by Mr. Spink to lay a lead flat in Fetter-lane. I have matched this lead to the flat, and believe it to belong to Mr. Spink's.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
